  "title": "Assistant Senior Stage Manager",
  "description": "<p>Job responsibilities : </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>· Assists in the recruitment and selection of performing artistes.   </p>\n<p>· Coordinates practices and rehearsal schedules for all performing artistes.   </p>\n<p>· Monitors and reports the work progress of all performing artistes.   </p>\n<p>. Manage the backstage and onstage area during performances.   </p>\n<p>· Conducts market research, gathers information on latest trends to improve business prospects.   </p>\n<p>· Plans, designs, and produces solutions while managing all project delivery elements within time limit. </p>\n<p>· Liaises with customers to identify their needs and to ensure customers’ satisfaction.   </p>\n<p>· Promotes the Company’s business via social media platforms.</p>",
